          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "HPGE"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The experiment was performed using six EURISYS",
                " high-purity germanium (HPGe) Clover detectors of the",
                " Livermore-Berkeley Array for Collaborative Experiments",
                " Each Clover consists of four HPGe crystals in a shared",
                " cryostat surrounded by 16 SCIONIX bismuth-germanate",
                " detectors. The system had high degree of segmentation",
                " with 19 HPGe and 94 BGO  detectors and good solid",
                " angle coverage."
